  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/9741e14e90f0c4e9c9ac39987e4d4749.poster.avif?t=1766096641\" width=612 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/9741e14e90f0c4e9c9ac39987e4d4749.webm?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/9741e14e90f0c4e9c9ac39987e4d4749.mp4?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world's memes are missing. You might be a washed up secret agent, but you're also the only one goated enough to save them. Grab a joint and step into an outrageous campaign where every boom headshot and 360 noscope brings you closer to unraveling the conspiracy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 missions of ridiculous combat and montage-worthy moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Egregious boss fights including the return of Sherk's swamp and Dhomas the dank engine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wave-based Endless mode to compete with your 'friends' who are probably SCRUBS!!!111</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hub world and armory to store your unlockable collection of crazy weapons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/ce579883cc9abc6c52fda9eade62fad4.poster.avif?t=1766096641\" width=612 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/ce579883cc9abc6c52fda9eade62fad4.webm?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/ce579883cc9abc6c52fda9eade62fad4.mp4?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >420BLAZEIT 2 features a healthy amount of IMAGINARY “consumables” that grant you cool powers so you can truly 420 BLAZE IT 360 NO SCOPE IT like an EPICC GAMER(™). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13 levels x 27 weapons x sherk + dhomas the dank engine = 420% BIGGER AND BETTER than the original!!1!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/b927f21bcc24e3a052a4fd1dff01dd12.poster.avif?t=1766096641\" width=612 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/b927f21bcc24e3a052a4fd1dff01dd12.webm?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/b927f21bcc24e3a052a4fd1dff01dd12.mp4?t=1766096641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This guy gets it</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624280/extras/ec2767a4b1ea2ce331874acb8cd2ef30.avif?t=1766096641\" width=330 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
